SUMMARY:The Ultimate St. Paddy's Day March 17th Dinner and DJ Bash!
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nGood day everyone\,\
 n\nPlease join us for a fantastic **St. Paddy's Dinner and DJ party** as w
 e mix\, mingle\, make new friends and then dance the night away to a fabul
 ous DJ! Playing all the best from the 70s\, 80s\, 90s\, 2000s and your req
 uests too!\n\n\\*Joined by my other social groups too\; so we can anticipa
 te a terrific turn out with lots of friendly peers to enjoy dinner and the
  lively dance floor!\n\n**Date:** Tuesday March 17th\, 2026\n**Location:**
  747 Mt. Pleasant (Smoke Show)\n\n**\\*Meet us inside Smoke Show between 6
 :00 pm and 7:30 pm (arrive later if you have too)**\n\\*If you have to arr
 ive after that\, still let the front door staff know you are with **Steve'
 s group** so they can direct you to us (but kindly do your best to arrive 
 between 6:00 pm and 7:30 pm -Thank you!\n(You will be paying me not the pe
 rson at the front door\, so simply ask them to direct you to the group- th
 ank you for your co-operation :)\n\n(Event Details Below)\n\nSincerely\,\n
 \nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host )\n\nEvent Details:\n**The Ultimate St. 
 Paddy's Day March 17th Dinner and DJ Bash!**\n\n-A fun\, interactive\, eve
 nt with friends\, food\, cocktails\, green beer (optional)\, reserved seat
 ing\, DJ and Dancing!\n-Pool Table available\n-DJ and Dancing after dinner
  :)\n-Plenty of parking all around the venue\n\\*For more information on t
 he menu please refer to the Smoke Show menu https://www.smokeshowbbqandbre
 w.com/\n\n**Event Fee:**\n5 dollars if you're **wearing green** (cash or i
 n advance by e transfer)\n10 dollars when you arrive not wearing green\n(c
 ash or e transfer in advance to [Steveflemming11@gmail.com](http://Stevefl
 emming11@gmail.com/))\n(Beverage or Appetizer Minimum please)\n\n**Friendl
 y Reminders:**\n**-Arrive any time between 6:00 pm and 7:30 pm inside the 
 restaurant (ask or look for Steve/Organizer when you arrive)**\n\\*If arri
 ving after 7:30 you still need to let the staff at the front know you are 
 with Steve's group so they can properly direct you to us- Thank you!\n\n\\
 *Just a 2 minute walk now from the new Eglinton and Mount Pleasant station
  :)
